<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c4">[١١٧٨٨]</span> وُهَيْبُ <span class="c2">(١)</span> بْنُ عَمْرٍو، أَبُو عَمْرٍو، النَّمَرِيُّ <span class="c2">(٢)</span> <span class="c2">(٣)</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>سَمِعَ هارُونَ النَّحْوِيَّ <span class="c2">(٤)</span>.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>رَوَى عَنْهُ رَوْحُ <span class="c2">(٥)</span> بْنُ عَبْدِ المُؤْمِنِ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
